s5RegMib.name: s5RegMib

revisions.description: Version 246: Added registrations for ERS 3550T and ERS 3550T-PWR+ models.
Version 245: Added registrations for ERS 5900 and ERS 4900 product families. They replace former X710 and X610.
Version 244: Added registrations for ERS X710 and ERS X610 product families.
Version 243: Added s5ChasComBrdGbic-DIRECT, s5ChasComBrdGbic-40G-SR4, s5ChasComBrdGbic-40G-LR, s5ChasComBrdGbic-40G-ER; added support for VSP7024XT and VSP7000 MDAs
Version 242: Added registrations for ERS3549GTS and ERS3549GTS-PWR+ models.
Version 241: Added registrations for 3526T and 3526T-PWR+ models.
Version 230: Added secondary flash registrations for ESU.
Version 229: Added CPU, Board1 and Board2 sensors for ESU. Added HW CPLD Store for ESU
Version 227: Added additional regs for 56xx pwr supplies.
Version 224: Added additional registrations for ERS56xx.
Version 223: Added registrations for new GBIC types.
Version 219: Added additional Botany Bay definitions.
v211: added s5ChasComBrdGbic-DWDM, s5ChasComBrdGbic-10G-SR, s5ChasComBrdGbic-10G-LR, s5ChasComBrdGbic-10G-ER, and s5ChasComBrdGbic-10G-LX4.
v210: added support for 2270 WLAN Security Switch Crypto Accelerator
v209: added support for Outrigger and Dragline.
v208: fixed typo & added support for 2270 WLAN Security Switch
v205: added support for Baystack 470 24T/48T PWR switches
